problem_info.title: 3370. Smallest Number With All Set Bits
test_examples: Example 1: Input: n = 5 Output: 7 Explanation: The binary representation of 7 is "111".
Example 2: Input: n = 10 Output: 15 Explanation: The binary representation of 15 is "1111".
Example 3: Input: n = 3 Output: 3 Explanation: The binary representation of 3 is "11".
